'''''Madame Satã''''' is a [[2002]] [[Brazil]]ian / [[France|French]] [[drama film]] directed by [[Karim Aïnouz]]. It tells the story of [[Madame Satã]] and [[premiere]]d at the [[Cannes Film Festival]].
